Sizes for monster types.
SIZ_NONE         For non-corpreal monsters (ghosts, shadows) No corpse left.
SIZ_TINY         For butterflies, goldfish, mice, rats...
SIZ_SMALL        For raccoons, dogs, cats, kobolds...
SIZ_MEDIUM       For Humanoids(Elves, Humands, Orcs...) Wolves...
SIZ_LARGE        For Bears, Lions, Trolls, Ettins...
SIZ_HUGE         For Dragons, Elephants, Whales, Titans...
